    <item>
      <title>副总统候选人提名临近 特朗普在迈阿密集会上调侃马尔科·卢比奥</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/trump-teases-marco-rubio-at-miami-rally-as-vp-announcement-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普在其迈阿密集会中注入了真人秀级别的戏剧性，多次暗示——但没有宣布——佛罗里达州参议员马尔科·卢比奥为竞选搭档，以期最大限度地吸引人们对其副总统候选人的关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/trump-teases-marco-rubio-at-miami-rally-as-vp-announcement-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 01:33:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基呼吁北约在美国大选前立即援助基辅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/zelenskiy-urges-nato-to-help-kyiv-now-before-the-us-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基呼吁北约盟国采取果断行动，帮助乌克兰击退俄罗斯的入侵，而不是“等到11月”，此言间接暗指美国总统大选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/zelenskiy-urges-nato-to-help-kyiv-now-before-the-us-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 00:13:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京将与多位世界领导人会面，为全球“弃儿”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/putin-is-meeting-a-lot-of-world-leaders-for-a-global-outcast</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统正在进行一系列外交活动，西方国家试图将他描绘成因乌克兰战争而陷入孤立的人，但结果却并非如此。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/putin-is-meeting-a-lot-of-world-leaders-for-a-global-outcast</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 00:00:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
